How to create linux and windows server in AWS console.
#step of Linux server#
Go to the EC2 serive--click on Launch instances--then give the server name and select Linux OS Image
scroll down & click on create new pair--Put key pair name then select private key file format(.pem)--click on create key pair
scroll down antique the allow SSH traffice form option then click Launch Instance.

After click on the launch instance linux seriver is ready but we cant access due to Firewall is available.
so we can enable SSH port for access the licux seriver find below step.
1)click on Instance ID --- scroll down click on Security and select security Group
2) click on Edit inbound rules--- click on Add rule.
3)select SSH in Type option (auto select 22 Port for SSH service)
4)select Anywhere- IPv4 then hit on the button Save rules

Now your Linux server is ready Use.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Step of Windows Seriver#
Go to the EC2 serive--click on Launch instances--then give the server name and select Windows OS Image
scroll down & click on create new pair--Put key pair name then select private key file format(.pem)--click on create key pair
scroll down antique the allow RDP traffice form option then click Launch Instance.

After click on the launch instance Windows seriver is ready but we cant access due to Firewall is available.
so we can enable RDP serive for access the windows server find below step.
1)click on Instance ID --- scroll down click on Security and select security Group
2) click on Edit inbound rules--- click on Add rule.
3)select RDP in Type option (auto select 3389 Port for RDP service)
4)select Anywhere- IPv4 then hit on the button Save rules
In this Case RDP serive create the password key
click on the instance id and connect-- select RDP Client-- Get password then upload private key file and select the file
click on Decrypt password (I%1XCxUqOs5S.0?pukbf9=9iOrZIEi2x)--Download remote desktop file

Now your Windows server is ready Use go to download option and click on windows server.rdp
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------









